WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.008
Because you are leading global enterprises, you face a unique

00:00:04.008 --> 00:00:08.016
challenge: the mechanics of trust and communication change drastically across

00:00:08.016 --> 00:00:12.024
borders. A global mindset allows you to understand the interdependence

00:00:12.024 --> 00:00:16.032
of the global economy, but Cultural Intelligence focuses on the

00:00:16.032 --> 00:00:20.040
behavioral ability to interact interpersonally and bridge cultural differences.
